                <h2>ASL Numbers 16 to 19</h2>

                <!-- Number 16 -->
                <p><strong>Number 16:</strong> Start with an open hand, then quickly form the handshape for 6 (thumb
                    touching pinky finger) as part of a fluid motion.</p>

                <!-- Number 17 -->
                <p><strong>Number 17:</strong> Start with an open hand, then quickly form the handshape for 7 (thumb
                    touching ring finger) as part of a fluid motion.</p>

                <!-- Number 18 -->
                <p><strong>Number 18:</strong> Start with an open hand, then quickly form the handshape for 8 (thumb
                    touching middle finger) as part of a fluid motion.</p>

                <!-- Number 19 -->
                <p><strong>Number 19:</strong> Start with an open hand, then quickly form the handshape for 9 (thumb
                    touching index finger) as part of a fluid motion.</p>
            </div>
