                </ul>

                <!-- Numbers 51-59 -->
                <p><strong>Numbers 51 to 59:</strong> Sign '5', followed by the respective unit numbers (1-9).</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>51:</strong> Start with the sign for '5', then sign '1' by extending the index finger.
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>52:</strong> Start with the sign for '5', then sign '2' by extending the index and
