                <!-- Number 90 -->
                <p><strong>Number 90:</strong> Sign '9' (thumb touching index finger) followed by the sign for '0' (an
                    'O' handshape).</p>

                <!-- Numbers 91-99 -->
                <p><strong>Numbers 91 to 99:</strong> Sign '9', followed by the respective unit numbers (1-9).</p>
