                    <li><strong>97:</strong> Start with the sign for '9', then sign '7' by touching the thumb to the
                        ring finger.</li>
                    <li><strong>98:</strong> Start with the sign for '9', then sign '8' by touching the thumb to the
                        middle finger.</li>
                    <li><strong>99:</strong> Start with the sign for '9', then sign '9' again.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

